--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Update
   ->  Partition Selector for rank_12402
         ->  Split
               ->  Result
                     ->  Hash Semi Join
                           Hash Cond: (rank_12402.value = rank1_12402_1.value)
